        "# Why this chapter\n",
        "\n",
        "This lecture gives the mathematical foundation you need for the rest of AD698.\n",
        "The goal is not abstract theorem proving; the goal is to make deep learning equations and code readable and intuitive.\n",
        "\n",
        "The structure in this chapter is adapted from the preliminaries sequence in Dive into Deep Learning [@zhang2023d2l], with additional SGD intuition and workflow guidance from DataCamp's SGD tutorial [@datacamp_sgd_tutorial].\n",
